data.description: Cozy home in the woods just waiting for you to enjoy the wonderful country life of the quiet Yonna Woods area of Bonanza. A double-sided propane fireplace will provide hours of enjoyment in your new living room and dining room as well as the Jacuzzi tub in the master bath. Not only is the home located on 4.69 acres but also includes a guest house and milking barn. Yonna Woods is a short commute into both Bonanza and Klamath Falls.
data.whatILove:
It’s very peaceful here. If you step outside after dark, I swear you could hear a pin drop. Everyone keeps to themselves. No arguments, no complaints and nobody argues over the fence. I’ve noticed in the past living in small towns, usually someone is arguing, houses broken into, dogs barking and nasty rumors spread, just to be mean or bored with their own lives.
Here in Yonna woods is just the opposite. But you had better love isolation. It’s all country and wildlife. A perfect spot for me and my husband.
